{"tid":1297010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真民主女神 何韻詩聯合國發言　兩度被中國代表打斷","createTime":"2019-07-08T13:59:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T15:50:06.000Z","uid":74778,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"83e8123a564e83df392ecad1bfb62715cdbec0db","tid":1297010,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:59:41.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n何韻詩聯合國發言　兩度被中國代表打斷<strong></strong></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n香港反送中運動持續，一直支持運動的歌手何韻詩，今日到瑞士日內瓦，在聯合國人權理事會的例會上發表兩分鐘演說，講解香港最新狀況，但她的發言兩度被中國代表打斷。<br />\n<br />\n何韻詩的發言主要圍繞香港反送中運動，指上月有 200 萬人上街，反對修例拆毀香港和中國的防火牆，但中國代表很快提出抗議，指香港是中華人民共和國的組成部份，形容何韻詩是「所謂 NGO 代表」，將香港與中國並列，違反了聯合國憲章。<br />\n<br />\n之後何韻詩繼續發言，指發送中運動中，已經有數十人被捕，四人自殺，成因是因為香港的高度自治不斷被蠶食，在北京的阻撓下香港至今仍未有普選，中方更否定中英聯合聲明的效力；中方代表再次提出抗議，指何韻詩不斷攻擊一國兩制制度，中方堅決反對，會議副主席討論後，繼續讓何韻詩發言，何韻詩最終呼籲聯合國，舉行緊急會議保護香港，又指中國不尊重人權，人權議會應將中國除名。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">句句中point<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BD%95%E9%9F%BB%E8%A9%A9%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%9C%8B%E7%99%BC%E8%A8%80-%E5%85%A9%E5%BA%A6%E8%A2%AB%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%89%93%E6%96%B7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BD%2595%25E9%259F%25BB%25E8%25A9%25A9%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25A8%2580-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%2596%25B7%2F&d=QWAfKg5qpFwl7mzrwQ2WUnpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=6819875c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BD%2595%25E9%259F%25BB%25E8%25A9%25A9%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25A8%2580-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%2596%25B7%2F&h=d295d8d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BD%95%E9%9F%BB%E8%A9%A9%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%9C%8B%E7%99%BC%E8%A8%80-%E5%85%A9%E5%BA%A6%E8%A2%AB%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%89%93%E6%96%B7/</a>"},{"pid":"6d91352c30ae1d235f052e77561f98de909084d9","tid":1297010,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:46:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf4585137c1216b377d88c293d7187ddee7401a6","tid":1297010,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:47:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/2654462571328449?s=754510061&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F715486135226112%2Fposts%2F2654462571328449%3Fs%3D754510061%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=QWAfKg5qpFwl7mzrwQ2WUnpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=ae5fbdc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/2654462571328449?s=754510061&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef60c79dae3e69de73fdf7df692cb20bd79d6b0d","tid":1297010,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:49:29.000Z","msg":"不過其實聯合國都奶共奶到霍霍有聲"},{"pid":"0be02a9fd604629a961b1b7881e7384c2c979e15","tid":1297010,"uid":160551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:50:06.000Z","msg":"最女 出現了"}]}